-- China May Bolster Energy-Saving Sector With Measures, Business News Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-20T00:48:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/china-may-bolster-energy-saving-sector-with-measures-business-news-says.html
China may this year issue a plan
with more measures to support the development of the energy-
savings industry after the State Council listed the industry as
one of seven new strategic industries, the China Business News
reported today, citing an unidentified person familar with the
situation.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
